rows.label: tev068601_MSG0001
rows.name:
Only those acknowledged by His Majesty Prince Jiarg
are permitted to speak of Lady Buidhe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0002
rows.name: I do not believe he has acknowledged you yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0007
rows.name:
True loyalty brooks no doubt. We all accede to His
Majesty's judgment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0008
rows.name: Even those abed from sickness would tell you the same.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0009
rows.name: Our suffering is transient. We will survive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0014
rows.name:
Long has Lady Buidhe served His Majesty.
She is his most trusted attendant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0015
rows.name:
Such sacrifice in service to one's lord is a mark of
great valor, even by the lofty standards of Wrothians.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0016
rows.name:
It is true that I laid down my own sword when I
married De Sazon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0017
rows.name:
But like Lady Buidhe, I would gladly offer my life upon
the battlefield should the opportunity present itself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0023
rows.name:
This medicine of yours is quite incredible.
Most of our sick have been saved.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0024
rows.name:
It is a relief that things turned out as they did.
As much as I value loyalty, the prospect of having to
sacrifice our innocent children was excruciating.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0025
rows.name:
But we kept our mouths sealed, lest we burden
His Majesty with complaints of our suffering.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0026
rows.name:
Thank you for all that you have done, human.
The debt we owe will not be forgotten.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0031
rows.name: My son is gone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0032
rows.name:
I do not know what your intentions were in helping
that boy, but this grudge will not be forgotten.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0033
rows.name: Not so long as I draw breath![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0038
rows.name: I am so grateful to you for returning my son to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0039
rows.name:
I shall rehabilitate him into a splendid warrior so that
your kindness will not have been in vain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068601_MSG0040
rows.name:
Never again will I be swayed to pity by his whining!
My heart shall be as black as a demon's.[ST:wait ]
